---
// Hero / header section: intro heading, bio, and portrait image.
---

<header
  class="relative mx-auto grid max-w-[1200px] grid-cols-1 items-center gap-8 px-8 pt-8 pb-20 desktop:grid-cols-2"
>
  <div class="content relative">
    <span class="blur"></span>
    <span class="blur"></span>
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-5xl font-bold leading-[4rem] text-white">
      Hi, I'm <span class="stroke">Nagy Richárd</span> Mechatronics engineering student
    </h1>
    <p class="mb-8 text-muted">
      Welcome to my website! I'm passionate about electronics, automation, robotics, and
      programming electrical devices.
      <br />
      <br />
      During high school, I self-taught a lot about embedded systems (Hardware - Software),
      industrial automation and robotics, which led me to compete in five competitions and
      participate in an Erasmus program. Currently, I'm pursuing a Mechatronics Engineering
      degree at Subotica Tech - College of Applied Sciences.
      <br />
      <br />
      I work as an Embedded Systems and Electrical Engineer at PIERRE, where I focus on
      designing custom hardware. When I'm not working on hardware, I develop firmware in C++
      to create innovative solutions.
      <br />
      <br />
      Let's connect! Feel free to reach out at richardnagy551@gmail.com and check out my
      projects on GitHub.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="image relative">
    <img src="/images/header.png" alt="Nagy Richárd" class="mx-auto flex max-w-[600px]" />
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  /* Blue accent glow, ported from .blur in style.css */
  .blur {
    position: absolute;
    box-shadow: 0 0 1000px 50px var(--color-accent);
    z-index: -100;
  }

  /* Outlined text for the name, ported from header .content h1 span */
  .stroke {
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px #fff;
  }

  /* Giant faint "o" watermark behind the portrait, ported from header .image::before */
  .image::before {
    content: 'o';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 38rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 20rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.2;
    z-index: -100;
  }

  @media (width < 600px) {
    .image::before {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
